<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((التعليق الرغيب)</span>) <span class="c2">(١/ ٢٠٥ ـ ٢٠٦)</span> , <span class="c2">((المشكاة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٦١٦٢)</span> , <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٦٩٦)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>